Huh? Chief?

517
00:43:20,924 --> 00:43:22,924
yes.

518
00:43:22,924 --> 00:43:24,924
📞Buds. On the move!

519
00:43:26,924 --> 00:43:31,924
Chief, you know, right? Today is an important day. Sorry!

520
00:43:31,924 --> 00:43:33,924
I want to go. Please pick it up! Momoko!

521
00:43:33,924 --> 00:43:35,924
I don't have time to get married after all.

522
00:43:35,924 --> 00:43:39,924
