Ah... I'm sorry, I had to cancel.

524
00:43:43,924 --> 00:43:47,924
Huh?! That's it... Hey Momoko! Momoko!

525
00:43:48,924 --> 00:43:51,924
Wait, Momoko! Won't you marry me!? It's an incident. Come quickly!

526
00:43:51,924 --> 00:43:54,924
Oh, I won't kiss you if you're late.

527
00:43:54,924 --> 00:43:56,924
Then dash! A fierce dash!

528
00:43:56,924 --> 00:43:58,924
Are you an elementary school student?

529
00:44:00,924 --> 00:44:03,924
Ah, here it comes... Go ahead!

530
00:44:05,924 --> 00:44:07,924
It's late. Thank you for your hard work.

531
00:44:07,924 --> 00:44:10,924
Thank you for your hard work. It's an incident.

532
00:44:10,924 --> 00:44:13,924
I don't think I'll be able to go home for 2-3 days this time either.

533
00:44:13,924 --> 00:44:15,924
Huh!? I haven't heard of it.

534
00:44:15,924 --> 00:44:17,924
Bud: I'll finish it quickly and go home. yes!

535
00:44:17,924 --> 00:44:19,924
(Suguro) Yes, materials. thank you.

536
00:44:19,924 --> 00:44:22,924
Have you decided on a dress? Canceled.

537
00:44:22,924 --> 00:44:24,924
(Akase, Mio, Suguro) Huh!? I haven't canceled it!

538
00:44:24,924 --> 00:44:27,924
I did. No, no, no...I won't let you cancel.

539
00:44:27,924 --> 00:44:29,924
Chief: Let's begin the investigation meeting.

540
00:44:29,924 --> 00:44:32,924
Okay. Chef, let's go!

541
